data.description: Property is sold as is, cash or investor loan only. Priced below market for a quick sale! One story with three bedrooms, two baths, on a good sized corner lot. Floorplan has living area, formal living area, and 4th bedroom option or 2nd living area from partially converted garage. Kitchen has double ovens and dishwasher. Vinyl flooring in entry and kitchen area, with carpet in bedrooms. Recent updates include newer roof, a/c system, and solar panels (original price of around 25k) installed in 2020. Some plumbing has been recently updated. Exterior has nice sized backyard and a good size covered patio that could be utilized as a Florida room potential. Close to IH-35, Loop 410, Fort Sam, Randolph AFB, Shopping & Schools.
